  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Technical Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Core responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Plan, organize and control Design operations to ensure efficient delegation of duties and responsibilities </li></ul><ul><li>Review project specifications, technical clarifications and construction drawings </li></ul><ul><li>Assist in tender preparations & technical submissions</li></ul><ul><li>Liaise with client’s representatives, consultants and subcontractors on technical matters</li></ul><ul><li>Prepare drawings for Authorities submission and approval</li></ul><ul><li>Provide advices to the project staffs for the details on the operation process and the material wastages control</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure designed quality of works is achieved and regulatory requirement are complied with</li></ul><ul><li>Able to forward quotation/costing on installation as request</li></ul><ul><li>Plan and implement training program for workforce</li></ul><p><strong>Job Specification </strong></p><p><strong>Minimum Educational Qualifications/ Experience required: </strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Electrical Engineering or its equivalent</li></ul><ul><li>Minimum 1 year in relevant experience</li></ul><ul><li>Experienced in designing and calculation for high/low voltage system of building projects </li></ul><ul><li>Experienced in coordination with clients, consultants for building projects </li></ul><ul><li>Status as a Qualified Person preferred\n </li><li>Good to have the BIM skill on crash and coordination solution knowledge</li></ul><p><strong>Special requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Knowledge on HT system, Transformer and LT switchgear, LV main feeder, Power distribution; Lighting and socket outlet, Low voltage system (Tel/Lan, Public address, Fire alarm, etc.)</li></ul><ul><li>Knowledge of Electrical Design Codes (Singapore CP, BS, NEC and NFPA) is essential </li></ul><ul><li>Able to propose VE items if necessary </li></ul><ul><li>Well-versed in MS Office and the latest version of AutoCad </li></ul><ul><li>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills</li></ul>",
